overview: RoommateRental.com is a free roommate matching, finder and search service which covers thousands of cities within United States, Canada, United Kingdom, and Ireland. Search for roommates, post your roommate ad or a room for rent ad. Browse through roommate listings with detailed profiles. Let us match you with the best roommates and rooms for rent! Whether you are a college student, a post graduate student, or even a professional looking for a suitable accommodation, all you need is to register with us. Each day hundreds of roommates/room finders and those who wish to rent out their apartment register with us.
